msgid "How to use this service from the command line"
msgstr "How to use this service from the command line"

msgid "You can use curl, httpie, wget, or whatever command line tool you prefer. Here's an example with curl:"
msgstr "You can use curl, httpie, wget, or whatever command line tool you prefer. Here's an example with curl:"

